[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":280},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220330\u002F766094107\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220330\u002F766094107\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220330\u002F766094107\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220330\u002F766094107\u002F":256,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220330\u002F766094107\u002F":265},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F03\u002F30\u002Fmango-frontend-27-mongodb-atlas-signup\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":237,"date":238,"description":18,"extension":239,"lang":240,"meta":241,"navigation":101,"path":242,"readingMinutes":243,"seo":244,"standalone":245,"stem":246,"tags":247,"tldr":253,"updated":253,"url":254,"__hash__":255},"content\u002F被迫吃芒果的前端工程師\u002F27-被迫吃芒果的前端工程師-Atlas-MongoDB-Atlas-申請.md","(27)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - Atlas - MongoDB Atlas 申請","766094107",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":231},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,34,41,44,48,51,57,60,63,69,72,109,112,118,121,127,130,133,136,139,142,145,151,154,160,163,169,172,178,181,185,188,194,197,203,206,212,215,218,224,227],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"那在接下來針對 MongoDB Atlas 稍微說明一下，這一篇也會紀錄下該如何申請 MongoDB Atlas。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"什麼是-mongodb-atlas","什麼是 MongoDB Atlas",[16,24,25],{},"MongoDB Atlas 基本上是 MongoDB 的一個雲端服務，讓你不用在電腦上安裝 MongoDB 就可以使用，為了避免你跑錯網站，所以建議你點以下連結進入官方網站",[16,27,28],{},[29,30,31],"a",{"href":31,"rel":32},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.mongodb.com\u002Fatlas\u002Fdatabase",[33],"nofollow",[16,35,36],{},[37,38],"img",{"alt":39,"src":40},"MongoDB Atlas","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2021.58.32%20(1).png",[16,42,43],{},"那麼接下來就來準備建立自己的 MongoDB Atlas 吧。",[12,45,47],{"id":46},"建立-mongodb-atlas","建立 MongoDB Atlas",[16,49,50],{},"那麼接下來透過上面連結進去到 MongoDB Atlas 官網後可以找一下畫面上有一個「Try Free」按鈕，按下去之後它會要你註冊，如果你有註冊過的話就直接登入。",[16,52,53],{},[37,54],{"alt":55,"src":56},"MongoDB Atlas 註冊","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.06.31.png",[16,58,59],{},"而這邊基本上我會使用 Google 登入（懶人）。",[16,61,62],{},"註冊之後它會問你一些問題，返正這個頁面就只是隱私條款頁面",[16,64,65],{},[37,66],{"alt":67,"src":68},"Accept Privacy Policy & Terms of Service","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.07.49.png",[16,70,71],{},"不負責翻譯：",[73,74,79],"pre",{"className":75,"code":76,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","接受隱私政策和服務條款\n請確認以下條款和條件以完成您的帳戶創建。\n\n我接受隱私政策和服務條款\n","cmd","",[80,81,82,90,96,103],"code",{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,84,87],"span",{"class":85,"line":86},"line",1,[83,88,89],{},"接受隱私政策和服務條款\n",[83,91,93],{"class":85,"line":92},2,[83,94,95],{},"請確認以下條款和條件以完成您的帳戶創建。\n",[83,97,99],{"class":85,"line":98},3,[83,100,102],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":101},true,"\n",[83,104,106],{"class":85,"line":105},4,[83,107,108],{},"我接受隱私政策和服務條款\n",[16,110,111],{},"按下允許之後會稍微等一下歡迎畫面",[16,113,114],{},[37,115],{"alt":116,"src":117},"歡迎畫面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.09.46.png",[16,119,120],{},"過一段時間之後它會要你填一些資料了解你用 MongoDB Atlas 要幹嘛",[16,122,123],{},[37,124],{"alt":125,"src":126},"MongoDB Atlas 要幹嘛","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.11.30.png",[16,128,129],{},"這邊也幫忙翻譯一下",[16,131,132],{},"Q: What is your goal today? Your answer will help us guide you to successfully getting started with MongoDB Atlas.\n(您今天的目標是什麼？您的回答將幫助我們指導您開始使用 MongoDB Atlas。)",[16,134,135],{},"A: Build a new application (建立一個應用程式)\nB: Migrate an existing application (遷移現有應用程式)\nC: Learn MongoDB (學習 MongoDB)\nD: Explore what I can build (搜尋我可以建立的內容)",[16,137,138],{},"Q: What type of application are you building? (您要建構什麼類型的應用程式？)\nA: 自己選一個吧。",[16,140,141],{},"Q: What is your preferred language? We’ll use this to customize code samples and content we share with you. You can always change this later.\n(您的開發語言是什麼？我們將使用它來產生範例程式碼範例的內容。後來你依然可以調整該設置）\nA: 當然是 JavaScript",[16,143,144],{},"輸入完畢之後就可以選擇資料庫類型啦~這邊當然要選 Free，畢竟只是練習而已",[16,146,147],{},[37,148],{"alt":149,"src":150},"Free DB","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.21.17.png",[16,152,153],{},"選擇資料庫之後就要開始部署雲端主機了",[16,155,156],{},[37,157],{"alt":158,"src":159},"選擇主機","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.23.10.png",[16,161,162],{},"主機基本上選 AWS 然後香港就好了",[16,164,165],{},[37,166],{"alt":167,"src":168},"AWS 主機","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.33.07.png",[16,170,171],{},"進入之後它會需要等待一下，所以你會在下方看到這個訊息",[16,173,174],{},[37,175],{"alt":176,"src":177},"等待訊息","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.34.46.png",[16,179,180],{},"當你看到上面那張圖之後，就代表你建立成功囉。",[12,182,184],{"id":183},"quickstart-資料庫","QuickStart 資料庫",[16,186,187],{},"接下來畫面上會需要設定一下使用者帳號密碼",[16,189,190],{},[37,191],{"alt":192,"src":193},"使用者帳號設定","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.44.35.png",[16,195,196],{},"底下這個使用者帳號密碼是很重要的，也就是等一下要讓你連接 MongoDB 用的帳號密碼，新增之後你也可以在底下看到",[16,198,199],{},[37,200],{"alt":201,"src":202},"帳號密碼","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.48.11.png",[16,204,205],{},"接下來下方我們也要設置允許的 IP，否則你無法遠端進去，因此這邊建議你按下「Add My Current IP Address」",[16,207,208],{},[37,209],{"alt":210,"src":211},"Add My Current IP Address","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2022.50.12.png",[16,213,214],{},"允許之後就可以按下 Finish and Close 囉~",[16,216,217],{},"當你看到以下畫面你就成功了",[16,219,220],{},[37,221],{"alt":222,"src":223},"Database Deployments","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-25%2023.06.52.png",[16,225,226],{},"那麼下一篇我們就準備資料庫囉",[228,229,230],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":78,"searchDepth":92,"depth":92,"links":232},[233,234,235,236],{"id":14,"depth":92,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":92,"text":22},{"id":46,"depth":92,"text":47},{"id":183,"depth":92,"text":184},"Nodejs","2022-03-30 16:01:48","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002F27-atlas-mongodb-atlas","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"被迫吃芒果的前端工程師\u002F27-被迫吃芒果的前端工程師-Atlas-MongoDB-Atlas-申請",[248,249,250,251,252,39],"Mongoose","MongoDB","Node.js","Mocha","被迫吃芒果的前端工程師",null,"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220330\u002F766094107\u002F","V0fa0W6olBSBpHZodcT6WBY1Wnt4331y7J4C2p7y82A",{"newer":257,"older":261},{"url":258,"title":259,"date":260},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F","(28)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - Atlas - MongoDB Compass 教學","2022-04-05 22:30:31",{"url":262,"title":263,"date":264},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220327\u002F434537006\u002F","(26)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - Mocha - MongoDB 讀取","2022-03-27 23:57:26",[266,270,275],{"url":267,"title":268,"date":269,"readingMinutes":243},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F","真是受夠開多個終端機執行多個指令了！來用 concurrently 吧","2026-01-13 09:45:28",{"url":271,"title":272,"date":273,"readingMinutes":274},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20250313\u002F3008873732\u002F","六角專題班學習組電商 API 之完整教學","2025-03-13 09:13:26","11",{"url":276,"title":277,"date":278,"readingMinutes":279},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20241225\u002F794319627\u002F","PM2 是 Process Manager 不是 PM2.5！","2024-12-25 1